text: Rajan Sawhney (born May 2, 1971) is a Canadian politician from the United Conservative Party in Alberta. She was elected in the 2019 Alberta general election to represent the electoral district of Calgary-North East in the 30th Alberta Legislature. == Awards == Rajan Sawhney has received the following awards.
